org.openbel.framework.common.record
Class Column<T>

java.lang.Object
  org.openbel.framework.common.record.Column<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
IntegerColumn, LongColumn, StringColumn
public abstract class Column<T>
extends Object

Represents a distinct data type within a record.

A column defines the data type's size, decoding, and encoding algorithms.

Author:
Nick Bargnesi
